  "precedence_rule": "Census relationship file wins on any disagreement. lee_building_permits.zip_code + NFIP reported_zipcode + collier owner/contractor_zip are MAILING-grade: candidate-only, admitted only if Census places the ZIP in a 6-county; all else excluded (G1/G7/moat). Site-grade published ZIPs (ZORI in-scope, collier_parcels.phy_zipcd, barrier table) are cross-checked for coverage, not used to widen scope.",
